                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                1. Flashing incorrect ROM may brick your device. Always backup first.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                2. Make sure device is in correct mode (Fastboot for most operations).
                                <LineBreak/>
                                3. Do not disconnect device during flash operation.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                4. Ensure battery is above 50% before flashing.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                5. Use only compatible ROM files for your device model.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="{StaticResource AccentBrush}">
                                This tool is provided as-is. Use at your own risk.
                                </Run>
                            </TextBlock>
                        </Grid>
                    </Border>
                </Grid>
